OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fafter alleged 'transphobic 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ftweets'                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, An ex-police officer has won a legal   
OL,6, challenge against a national policy for
OL,7, forces to record gender-critical views 
OL,8, as non-crime "hate incidents".         
OL,10,FHumberside Police visited Harry Miller 
OL,11,Fin January 2020 after a complaint over 
OL,12,Falleged transphobic tweets he made.    
OL,14,FIt was recorded on a national database 
OL,15,Fas a non-crime hate incident.          
OL,17,FBut the Court of Appeal ruled on Monday
OL,18,Fthe guidance was wrongly used and it   
OL,19,Fhad a "chilling effect" on Mr Miller's 
OL,20,Ffreedom of speech.                     
